column2:
Thank you for agreeing to participate in our data collection. For this task, you are showing a home organizing robot how to tidy your home by demonstrating your preferred placement locations for each object image. Referring to the home layout we have provided you, please provide 1-3 locations for each object.

For each placement, choose a room from the drop down menu (e.g. kitchen, living room, etc.) and type in the letter from the layout to show where you would like to place the object (e.g. A, B, etc.).
